scene.message:
Yosuke: Is it really{nl}
{ctl0f:1}? I never thought{nl}
I'd meet you all again!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: What?{nl}
Could you be...{nl}
the missing Naito?!{waitkey}{ret}

Yosuke: Yeah!{nl}
I drifted here 2 months{nl}
ago — with Chisato...{waitkey}Kasai-san.{nl}
Same world as you!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: You said "world"...{wait_fr:60}{nl}
This isn't the past,{nl}
but another dimension?{waitkey}{ret}

Yosuke: Yeah, I thought{nl}
it was the past at first.{nl}
Looked just like our town.{waitkey}{clearbox}But parts were off —{nl}
the police station was{nl}
a forest, the hospital{waitkey}a diner.{nl}
And Maki, as you see.{nl}
It was like paradise...{waitkey}{wait_fr:88}until a month ago.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: A parallel world...{nl}
Worlds like ours existing{nl}
in parallel universes...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Seriously...{nl}
I thought you eloped{nl}
with Kasai!{waitkey}{clearbox}But you went to{nl}
another world! That's wild —{nl}
but wait, same goes for us.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Fantastic!{nl}
How wonderful!{nl}
Like a novel or movie!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Seriously?!{nl}
Ayase has things to do!{nl}
What do we do, {ctl0f:1}?!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: No way!{nl}
How do we get back?!{nl}
Ugh...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hard to believe,{nl}
but given the DEVA System,{nl}
accepting it seems right.{waitkey}{ret}

Yosuke: Well, that's{nl}
understandable...{wait_fr:92}{nl}
But for this world's Maki{nl}
to bring you all here...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Wait!{nl}
So Sonoda is Sonoda,{nl}
but not our Sonoda?!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I'm sorry!{nl}
I wasn't trying to{nl}
deceive you!{waitkey}{clearbox}I wasn't sure until{nl}
we got back. I never{nl}
thought another world{waitkey}was real and that I'd{nl}
go there...{nl}
I planned to tell you after.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: I see.{nl}
No wonder her behavior{nl}
was strange.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I dozed off in class{nl}
and woke in another world.{nl}
It took a while to realize.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Unbelievable...{nl}
The real Sonoda is still{nl}
in the hospital...{waitkey}{clearbox}May I say one thing?{nl}
Uh...{wait_fr:108} Sonoda.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Sorry, but would{nl}
you have believed me?{waitkey}{clearbox}And if we beat Kandori,{nl}
both worlds should{nl}
return to normal...{waitkey}I planned to tell{nl}
you after, I promise.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I see...{nl}
Hmm? Kasai's not here —{nl}
where is she?{waitkey}{ret}

Yosuke: Chisato...{nl}
Kasai-san was taken{nl}
by that black girl...{waitkey}{wait_fr:88}Damn!{waitkey}{ret}

Dark girl's voice: Kyahaha!{nl}
This time I'll wreck{nl}
this school for sure!{waitkey}{clearbox}I hid the exits so{nl}
no one can escape!{nl}
Kyahahahahahaha...{waitkey}{ret}

Yosuke: No doubt it's her!{nl}
She erased the exit?!{nl}
If demons come now...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Stop! Yosuke-kun!{nl}
Please, don't{nl}
push yourself!{waitkey}Everyone, help!{nl}
We have to do{nl}
something!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Not sure what's{nl}
happening, but we're{nl}
stuck! Let's go, {ctl0f:1}!{waitkey}{ret}

Yosuke: Damn!{nl}
If my body cooperated,{nl}
I could save Chisato!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hm? This injury?{nl}
{wait_fr:88}When she last came{nl}
she beat me badly...{waitkey}What a sorry state{nl}
I'm in!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: She must be{nl}
somewhere in school!{waitkey}Don't underestimate{nl}
her size — she has{nl}
strange powers!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What connects{nl}
that girl and Kandori?{nl}
Too little data to judge...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: No use worrying!{nl}
To find a way back,{nl}
handle this first!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Ugh...{nl}
is there really{nl}
a way back...?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: {ctl0f:1},{nl}
make sure you find{nl}
a way home, okay?!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: A girl who{nl}
commands demons...{nl}
A Devil Summoner?{waitkey}{ret}

{color:2}Naito Yosuke.{nl}
A playboy missing for{nl}
2 months with Kasai.{color:0}{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I see...{nl}
So Kasai is still held{nl}
by that black girl?{waitkey}{ret}

Yosuke: Yeah...{nl}
and I couldn't even{nl}
protect her...{waitkey}{wait_fr:88}Damn!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: ...{nl}
Kandori's kid, you say?{nl}
He has no kids.{waitkey}{ret}
